# why it's show red => when i add pnpm-lock.yaml to .gitignore, it will show red because it is ignored by git, but it is still there in the project directory. If you want to remove it from the project directory, you can run the command "git rm --cached pnpm-lock.yaml" to remove it from git tracking, and then commit the changes. After that, it will no longer show red in your code editor.
